OL,4,G0100FThe Yorkshire Vet
OL,5,     GJulian heads to the Taylors'
OL,6,     Gfarm. One of their sheep has
OL,7,     Gprolapsed a few days after he
OL,8,     Gdelivered her lamb. 8-week old
OL,9,     GShih Tzu puppy Lester needs
OL,10,     Gsurgery on a troublesome hernia.
OL,11,G0200FCruising with Jane McDonald
OL,12,     GJane and friends continue their
OL,13,     Gcelebration trip along the River
OL,14,     GThames, where they set sail for a
OL,15,     GMichelin three-starred
OL,16,     Grestaurant, before ending the
OL,17,     Gcruise at Henley-on Thames.
